data.description: This home sits on a large corner lot and features 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, updated flooring and more.  The furnace has been upgraded as well as the hot water heater and there is a large master suite right off the living room.   The patio is covered and there is a storage shed.   The updated kitchen will make this a nice home for all the gatherings.  This home will have a new roof installed prior to closing. SOLD AS IS.
